dct_title_s: Map to accompany a Journey from Inhambane to Zoutpansberg, in 1855-6
dct_description_sm: by James Mc.Queen, Esqr. F.R.G.S. ; Pubd. for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Socy. by J. Murray, Albemarle Strt. London, 1862.
Shows waterways, towns, routes, various place names.
Descriptive text, such as "Very high-snow at times."
Journal of the Royal Geographic Society, volume 32, between pages 62-63.
